    <div class="rwrap">
      <header class="sec__head" data-reveal>
        <span class="meta right">5 · 7 · 9 day plans · supervised</span>
        <span class="meta no">03 · Panchakarma</span>
        <p class="kicker">Ayurvedic Wellness Centre</p>
        <h2>14 Years of Authentic Ayurvedic Healing: <em>Panchakarma Detox Therapy</em> in Sydney</h2>
        <img class="flourish" src={separator} alt="" width="398" height="36" loading="lazy" />
        <p class="lede">Has your busy schedule left you feeling the need to cleanse and rejuvenate your body and mind? Ancient Ayurvedic Panchakarma Detox therapy helps eliminate toxins, improve digestion, boost energy levels and strengthen the immune system.</p>
      </header>

      <div class="entry" data-reveal>
        <span class="entry__no">01</span>
        <div class="entry__text">
          <h3>What Is Panchakarma Detox?</h3>
          <p>Ayurveda believes that the buildup of toxins in the tissues and blockage of channels of circulation are the root cause of many chronic conditions.</p>
          <p>Panchakarma Detox is a therapeutic system that cleanses toxins that are already in your body and are the underlying cause of health imbalances and diseases.</p>
          <p>Ayurveda has used these cleansing treatments to rejuvenate the mind and body since ancient times. Book a treatment and discover the difference Panchakarma can make to your wellbeing.</p>
          <a class="ilink ilink--gold" href="/services/panchakarma-ayurvedic-detox-sydney/">Find Out More ›</a>
        </div>
        <figure class="plate plate--dark">
          <img src="/wp-content/uploads/elementor/thumbs/©CliquePhotographySydney_G4H4474_Edit-rkuf574i9372gylbszubqtan2hqqdz66wrlvg4zp0w.jpg" alt="©CliquePhotographySydney_G4H4474_Edit" width="600" height="600" loading="lazy" />
          <figcaption><span class="fig">fig. 2 — herbal poultice, in the rooms</span></figcaption>
        </figure>
      </div>

      <div class="entry" data-reveal>
        <span class="entry__no">02</span>
        <div class="entry__text">
          <h3>Why Choose Panchakarma Detox?</h3>
          <p>For 14 years, Ayurvedic Wellness Centre has been helping Sydney clients transform their health with authentic Panchakarma Detox Therapy. This ancient Ayurvedic program combines therapeutic massages, herbal treatments, and gentle cleansing procedures that work synergistically to restore balance and promote overall wellbeing.</p>
          <p>This ancient Ayurvedic therapy helps to:</p>
          <ul class="benefits" role="list">
            <li>Eliminate toxins</li>
            <li>Improve digestion</li>
            <li>Boost energy levels</li>
            <li>Enhance mental clarity</li>
            <li>Promote weight loss</li>
            <li>Boost healthy skin and complexion</li>
            <li>Strengthen the immune system</li>
          </ul>
          <p>You can look forward to improved health, vitality and a renewed sense of wellness after your treatment.</p>
          <a class="rbtn rbtn--gold" href="/book-appointment/">Book Your Appointment</a>
        </div>
        <figure class="plate plate--dark">
          <img src="/wp-content/uploads/elementor/thumbs/MEDITATION-ROOM-1-rkuf574i9372gylbszubqtan2hqqdz66wrlvg4zp0w.webp" alt="Ayurveda Experiences in Bondi Junction, Sydney" width="600" height="600" loading="lazy" />
          <figcaption><span class="fig">fig. 3 — the meditation room</span></figcaption>
        </figure>
      </div>

      <div class="entry" data-reveal>
        <span class="entry__no">03</span>
        <div class="entry__text">
          <h3>Longer Treatments For Deeper, More Holistic Cleansing</h3>
          <p>Ayurveda says that when Panchakarma treatments are administered daily for several days in a row, cleansing begins to occur at a deeper level.</p>
          <p>According to Ayurveda, a 7-Day treatment is ideal as it is believed to sequentially cleanse and rejuvenate all 7 major bodily tissues.</p>
          <p>At the Ayurvedic Wellness Centre, these treatments are offered under the supervision of our highly qualified and experienced Ayurvedic practitioners.</p>
          <p>Contact us for a bespoke treatment plan, which could be a 5-day, 7-day, 9-day plan based on your current level of wellbeing.</p>
